# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchDates/welchmoviedate.rpy:14
translate portuguese welchmoviedate_ba301308:

    # "I go to the theater and find Nora already sitting in the back, waiting for me."
    "Vou ao cinema e encontro a Nora já sentada lá atrás, à minha espera."

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchDates/welchmoviedate.rpy:16
translate portuguese welchmoviedate_994bf3fa:

    # sst "Hey, [pcname]. What a funny coincidence seeing you here. Want to join me for a completely platonic, friendly movie?"
    sst "Olá, [pcname]. Que coincidência engraçada ver-te aqui. Queres juntar-te a mim para um filme totalmente platónico e amigável?"

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchDates/welchmoviedate.rpy:17
translate portuguese welchmoviedate_3a85a17a:

    # pc "Absolutely, Ms. Welch, that sounds very nice."
    pc "Claro, Sra. Welch, isso parece-me muito bem."

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchDates/welchmoviedate.rpy:18
translate portuguese welchmoviedate_c80f153e:

    # sst "I didn't see anybody that I recognized, so hopefully we're in the clear here."
    sst "Não vi ninguém que reconhecesse, por isso espero que estejamos a salvo aqui."

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchDates/welchmoviedate.rpy:19
translate portuguese welchmoviedate_6f039882:

    # sst "We have a little time to chat before the movie starts."
    sst "Temos um tempinho para conversar antes do filme começar."

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchDates/welchmoviedate.rpy:25
translate portuguese welchmoviedate_20b3a8b1:

    # "When the movie starts the room gets dark and we stop talking."
    "Quando o filme começa, a sala escurece e paramos de falar."

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchDates/welchmoviedate.rpy:30
translate portuguese welchmoviedate_fd60e14c:

    # "She reaches over and holds my hand on top of the arm rest."
    "Ela estende a mão e segura a minha em cima do apoio de braço."

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchDates/welchmoviedate.rpy:31
translate portuguese welchmoviedate_aee76b2d:

    # "The trailers take up about fifteen minutes, then the movie really gets started."
    "Os trailers duram cerca de quinze minutos, depois o filme começa de verdade."

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchDates/welchmoviedate.rpy:36
translate portuguese welchmoviedate_13c96bc1:

    # "Once she gets comfortable in the dark, more assured that nobody is going to recognize us, she leans against my shoulder and I put my arm around her."
    "Assim que ela se sente à vontade no escuro, mais segura de que ninguém vai nos reconhecer, ela encosta-se no meu ombro e eu coloco o meu braço à sua volta."

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchDates/welchmoviedate.rpy:41
translate portuguese welchmoviedate_5e156393:

    # "About halfway through the movie, we both completely lose interest and start making out, barely able to control ourselves."
    "A meio do filme, ambos perdemos completamente o interesse e começamos a beijar-nos, mal conseguindo controlar-nos."

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchDates/welchmoviedate.rpy:46
translate portuguese welchmoviedate_739549ff:

    # "Then when the movie ends and the lights come on, we force ourselves to separate from each other, just in case anybody sees us."
    "Depois, quando o filme acaba e as luzes se acendem, forçamo-nos a separar-nos, para o caso de alguém nos ver."

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchDates/welchmoviedate.rpy:47
translate portuguese welchmoviedate_578a20f5:

    # sst "Do you remember anything that happened in the second half of that movie?"
    sst "Lembras-te de alguma coisa que tenha acontecido na segunda metade daquele filme?"

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchDates/welchmoviedate.rpy:48
translate portuguese welchmoviedate_17f6f9d6:

    # pc "I don't even remember what the movie was called."
    pc "Eu nem me lembro do nome do filme."

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchDates/welchmoviedate.rpy:49
translate portuguese welchmoviedate_62a98bcd:

    # sst "Ha, we're awful."
    sst "Ha, somos horríveis."

translate portuguese strings:

    # game/Scenes/Welch/WelchDates/welchmoviedate.rpy:2
    old "In the evening on the weekend after the scene where you almost get caught fucking Ms. Welch in class,"
    new "À noite, no fim de semana, depois da cena em que quase foste apanhado a foder a Sra. Welch na aula,"

    # game/Scenes/Welch/WelchDates/welchmoviedate.rpy:3
    old "she will call you and ask if you want to meet up at the movie theater."
    new "ela vai ligar-te e perguntar se queres encontrar-te com ela no cinema."

